Package automation.pages

Class LoginPage

  • java.lang.Object
    • automation.utils.DefaultLogger
      • automation.utils.PageTools
        • automation.pages.LoginPage
  • public class LoginPage
extends PageTools
    The LoginPage class represents the login page of the application. It provides methods to interact with the login page elements such as entering a username, entering a password, clicking the login button, and verifying if the login page is displayed.

    This class extends PageTools to leverage common Selenium utilities.
